{"word":"ἀέξω","slug":"ἀέξω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n1703\" key=\"a)e/cw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀέξω</orth>, poet. form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὔξω </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">αὐξάνω</etym>), once in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author></bibl>, twice in Trag. (lyr.); in early writers only in <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and unaugm. <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns>: in later Poets <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ fut.\">fut.</a></tns> <sense id=\"n1703.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀεξήσω</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Nonn.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.24</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἠέξησα</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:104\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.104</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.787</biblScope> </bibl> (Troezen, <date TEIform=\"date\">iv A. D.</date>): <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ fut.\">fut.</a></tns> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀεξήσομαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:837\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.837</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀεξήθην</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.631</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Agath.\">Agath.</a></author> </bibl>): <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ plpf.\">plpf.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ηέξητο </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀν-</etym>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:427\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Nonn.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.427</biblScope> </bibl>: (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀϝέξω</foreign>, cf. Lat. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">augeo</tr_>, Skt. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">vak[snull ]áyati</tr_>, etc.):—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">increase, foster.</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀνδρὶ δὲ κεκμηῶτι μένος μέγα οἶνος ἀέξει</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:261\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.261</biblScope> </bi